snippet.title: Banishers: Ghosts of New Eden - Extended Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Pre-order Banishers: Ghosts of New Eden now: https://store.focus-entmt.com/w/banishersghostsofneweden?utm_campaign=Banishers_ExtendedGameplayTrailer&utm_medium=description&utm_source=YouTube

In a world where the souls of the departed roam, you play a couple of Banishers. Antea Duarte and Red mac Raith. Combine Antea’s spiritual powers and Red’s powerful arsenal to defeat and banish the souls that torment the living. Uncover secrets, navigate mysterious landscapes, and meet memorable but tormented characters whose fate rests in your hands.

Will you honor your Banisher oath or sacrifice the living in a desperate bid to bring your beloved back ?
Banishers: Ghosts of New Eden releases November 7th  to PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X|S and PC, and pre-orders are now available on all platforms, with a Collector’s Edition and the newly revealed Red Echoes Edition exclusive to the Focus Store!
